msgid "// x is of type &u32\n"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2024/intoiterator-box-slice.md:71
msgid "to be:"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2024/intoiterator-box-slice.md:82
msgid ""
"The [`boxed_slice_into_iter`](../../rustc/lints/listing/warn-by-default."
"html#boxed-slice-into-iter) lint is defaulted to warn on all editions, so "
"unless you have manually silenced the lint, you should already see it before "
"you migrate."
msgstr ""
